data.text: @PMBarraclough @JoshButler @MSMWatchdog2013 Ok, I give up now. I am not “exercised” at all.  I am not engaging any more though.

@jasonandrade @JoshButler @MSMWatchdog2013 I was a journalist in the press gallery, so ..  yes. Less so now I am old . This dude is Minister for State, amongst other roles, and I merely expressed surprisenot to have heard of him, seen him on question time or anywhere else. I don’t know why you are so exercised by this?

@PMBarraclough @JoshButler @MSMWatchdog2013 I am now genuinely curious. 

Did you honestly keep track of the 42 (no typo) separate ministers in the government *and* all the shadow ministers too? 

Even just Cabinet is 24 ministers with 32 separate portfolios. 

I couldn’t even name all 32 Portfolios without looking it up.
@PMBarraclough @JoshButler @MSMWatchdog2013 One of the 'quiet Australians' who loves his Prime Minister.

@PMBarraclough @JoshButler @MSMWatchdog2013 Who?

Can't say that it's a name that I've heard of before 🤔
@jasonandrade @JoshButler @MSMWatchdog2013 This is my least grammatical tweet ever, I blame the steroids I’m taking ..

@JoshButler Hello Josh
Has he been seen anywhere near Jane Hume?
